xit paths\\n- **Good `isDisconnected` exit code handling**: Correctly distinguishes exit 1 (no ancestor) from actual errors\\n- **Thorough diff parser testing**: Good coverage of `parseDiffTreeOutput` with edge cases (renames, copies, mixed ops)\\n- **Project conventions followed**: `t.Parallel()`, `t.Helper()`, proper file organization\\n\\n## Recommended Action\\n\\n1. Fix critical issues #1-3 (reconciliation failure handling in push path, doctor exit code, filesChangedInCommit fallback)\\n2. Address important issues #4-5 (add debug logging to WarnIfMetadataDisconnected, consider writer parameter)\\n3. Add missing test cases (#7-8) for depth limit and all-empty-orphans\\n4. Consider suggestions as time permits\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":42,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":8995,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":74211,\"output_tokens\":1260,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":8995,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYivP5CXdM2evp6rmaB6G\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"8bd528db-6158-4b3c-ab20-8e728c56b47e\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T23:39:03.917Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"8bd528db-6158-4b3c-ab20-8e728c56b47e\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/3\",\"sessionId\":\"042ac44f-5efd-4c35-8e56-7fedf6e12548\",\"version\":\"2.1.66\",\"gitBranch\":\"fix/reconcile-disconnected-metadata-branch\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks claude-code stop\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"9dafd358-968a-4560-a0b9-a621799e39cd\",\"toolUseID\":\"9dafd358-968a-4560-a0b9-a621799e39cd\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T23:39:03.958Z\",\"uuid\":\"aa4e1271-bc85-4063